'''Giuseppe Barcella''' (13 June 1926 - 8 February 1992) was an Italian [[philatelist]] who signed the [[Roll of Distinguished Philatelists]] in 1990.<ref>''[http://www.abps.org.uk/Awards/Roll_of_Distinguished_Philatelists/RDP_Background_20111231_LR.pdf Background notes on The Roll of Distinguished Philatelists September 2011]'', Roll of Distinguished Philatelists Trust, London, 2011. [https://www.webcitation.org/6OlHSBOTl Archived here.]</ref>

