'''James Mayer''' (1920–1944) was a [[Mauritian]] secret agent during [[World War II]].<ref>* Fiche James Mayer : voir le site [http://www.specialforcesroh.com/browse.php?mode=viewiroll&rollid=4077 Special Forces Roll of Honour]</ref><ref>J.D. Sainsbury, ''Le Mémorial de la section F'', Gerry Holdsworth Special Forces Charitable Trust, 1992</ref><ref>Lt. Col. E.G. Boxshall, ''Chronology of SOE operations with the resistance in France during world war II'', 1960, document dactylographié (exemplaire en provenance de la bibliothèque de [[Pearl Witherington|Pearl Witherington-Cornioley]], consultable à la bibliothèque de Valençay). Voir sheet 54, CARVER CIRCUIT.</ref>

