hel Santesso &#124; Credits |publisher=AllMusic |date= |accessdate=2016-01-08}}</ref> |- | 2011 | ''[[Rabbits on the Run]]'' | Razor & Tie | [[Vanessa Carlton]], primary artist; Rachel Santesso, choir director<ref name="allmusic1"/> |- | 2015 | ''[[Pan (2015 film)|Pan]] Original Motion Picture Soundtrack'' | [[Warner Bros]] | Rachel Santesso; choir master |}
