{{Orphan|date=January 2013}} {{Infobox football biography | name = Tarko Islamov | fullname = Tarko Alikhanovich Islamov | image = Tarko sub.jpg | image_size = 220 | caption = Tarko debuting for FC Terek youth squad, May 5, 2009 | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1991|6|22|mf=yes}} | birth_place = [[Grozny]], [[Chechen Republic]], [[Russia]] | height = {{height|m=1.77}} | currentclub = [[FC Terek Grozny]] | clubnumber = 51 | position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]] | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = 2009– | clubs1 = [[FC Terek Grozny]] | caps1 = 0 | goals1 = 0 | nationalyears1 = | nationalteam1 = | nationalcaps1 = | nationalgoals1 = | club-update = 11:05, July 17, 2010 (UTC) | nationalteam-update = }}
'''Tarko Alikhanovich Islamov''' ({{lang-ru|Тарко Алиханович Исламов}}, born June 22, 1991) is a [[Russia]]n footballer who currently plays for the [[Russian Premier League]] team [[FC Terek Grozny]].
==Career== Islamov made his professional debut for [[FC Terek Grozny]] on 13 July 2010 in the [[Russian Cup (football)|Russian Cup]] game against [[FC Luch-Energiya Vladivostok]].
==External links== * {{ru icon}} [http://fc-terek.ru/index.php?option=com_joomleague&func=showPlayer&p=10&pid=84&Itemid=88888943 Player page on the official FC Terek Grozny website] * {{ru icon}} [http://www.rfpl.org/player/id12646 Player page on the official Russian Premier League website]
